        This website uses Microsoft Clarity, a web analytics service provided by Microsoft.
        Microsoft Clarity helps understand how visitors interact with the website through
        session recordings, heatmaps, and usage analytics.
    </p>

    <p>
        Clarity may automatically collect certain information including:
    </p>

    <ul>
        <li>Pages visited</li>
        <li>Clicks, scrolling, and interaction behavior</li>
        <li>Browser and device type</li>
        <li>Approximate geographic location</li>
