    <p>
        This website may use cookies to collect analytics data and improve the browsing
        experience. Cookies are small text files stored on your device by your browser.
    </p>

    <p>
        You can choose to disable cookies through your browser settings if you prefer
        not to allow them.
    </p>

    <h2>Use of Information</h2>
    <p>
        Information collected through analytics is used only for the following purposes:
    </p>

    <ul>
        <li>Understanding how visitors use the website</li>
        <li>Improving website usability and performance</li>
        <li>Analyzing traffic trends</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
        This website does not collect personal information such as names, phone numbers,
        or payment details.
    </p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>
        This website uses Microsoft Clarity for analytics purposes. Microsoft may process
